  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    A[Replication Fork] --> B[DnaB Helicase]\n    B --> C[DNA Unwinding]\n    C --> D[Single-Stranded DNA Regions]\n    D --> E{Strand Type?}\n    \n    E -->|Leading Strand| F[Continuous Synthesis Template]\n    E -->|Lagging Strand| G[Discontinuous Synthesis Template]\n    \n    %% Leading Strand Pathway\n    F --> H[DNA Pol III Core Enzyme \u03b1]\n    H --> I[3'-OH Primer Terminus]\n    I --> J{dNTP Available?}\n    J -->|Yes| K[Nucleotide Selection]\n    J -->|No| L[Synthesis Paused]\n    \n    K --> M[Watson-Crick Base Pairing]\n    M --> N[Phosphodiester Bond Formation]\n    N --> O[Pyrophosphate Release]\n    O --> P[DNA Extension +1 Nucleotide]\n    P --> Q{Proofreading Check?}\n    \n    Q -->|Correct Base| R[Continue Synthesis]\n    Q -->|Mismatch| S[3'-5' Exonuclease \u03b5 Subunit]\n    S --> T[Excise Incorrect Nucleotide]\n    T --> K\n    \n    R --> U[Beta Clamp Processivity]\n    U --> V[Tau Clamp Loader]\n    V --> W[Maintain Association]\n    W --> X{End of Template?}\n    X -->|No| K\n    X -->|Yes| Y[Leading Strand Complete]\n    \n    %% Lagging Strand Pathway\n    G --> Z[SSB Coating ssDNA]\n    Z --> AA[DnaG Primase Recognition]\n    AA --> AB[RNA Primer Synthesis]\n    AB --> AC[~10 nt RNA Primer]\n    AC --> AD[DNA Pol III Recognition]\n    \n    AD --> AE{Okazaki Fragment Synthesis?}\n    AE -->|Initiate| AF[DNA Pol III Core Enzyme \u03b1]\n    AF --> AG[Extension from RNA Primer]\n    AG --> AH[dNTP Incorporation]\n    AH --> AI[Synthesis ~1000-2000 nt]\n    \n    AI --> AJ{Reach Previous Fragment?}\n    AJ -->|No| AH\n    AJ -->|Yes| AK[Pol III Dissociates]\n    \n    AK --> AL[DNA Pol I Recognition]\n    AL --> AM[5'-3' Exonuclease Activity]\n    AM --> AN[Nick Translation]\n    AN --> AO[Remove RNA Primer]\n    AO --> AP[Replace with DNA]\n    \n    AP --> AQ{Nick Remaining?}\n    AQ -->|Yes| AR[DNA Ligase]\n    AR --> AS[Seal Phosphodiester Backbone]\n    AS --> AT[Completed Okazaki Fragment]\n    \n    %% Coordination and Regulation\n    AT --> AU{New Primer Needed?}\n    AU -->|Yes| AA\n    AU -->|No| AV[Lagging Strand Complete]\n    \n    B --> AW{Helicase-Primase Coordination?}\n    AW -->|Signal| AA\n    \n    U --> AX{Leading-Lagging Coupling?}\n    V --> AX\n    AX -->|Coordinated| AY[Replisome Integrity]\n    \n    AY --> AZ{Continue Replication?}\n    L --> AZ\n    AZ -->|Fork Active| BA[Processive Synthesis]\n    AZ -->|Fork Stalled| BB[Checkpoint Activation]\n    \n    BA --> BC{Obstacles?}\n    BC -->|Lesions| BD[Lesion Bypass Pathways]\n    BC -->|Proteins| BE[Fork Remodeling]\n    BC -->|None| K\n    \n    BD --> BF[TLS Polymerases]\n    BE --> BG[Recombination Pathways]\n    \n    Y --> BH{Both Strands Complete?}\n    AV --> BH\n    BH -->|Yes| BI[Replicated DNA Duplex]\n    BH -->|No| BA\n    \n    BI --> BJ[Topoisomerase Resolution]\n    BJ --> BK(\\1)\n    BK --> BL[Sister Chromosome Separation]\n    \n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style G fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style H fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style L fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style M fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style N fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style O fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style P fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Q fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style R fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style S fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style T fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style Y fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style Z fil