  "name": "DNA Replication Elongation",
  "notGates": 0,
  "notes": "Comprehensive flowchart of E. coli DNA replication elongation showing coordination between leading and lagging strand synthesis, proofreading mechanisms, Okazaki fragment processing, and replisome integrity. Based on decades of biochemical and structural research.",
