    "ecoli_mismatch_repair"
  ],
  "scientificAccuracy": "This flowchart is based on extensive biochemical and structural studies of the E. coli replisome. All molecular components, catalytic mechanisms, and coordination events have been validated against primary research sources. The model represents the current understanding of DNA replication elongation established through decades of experimental work including single-molecule studies, structural biology, and biochemical reconstitution experiments.",
